{"tid":1271324,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」 雞蛋策略其實仲可行","createTime":"2019-07-01T06:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T11:41:08.000Z","uid":73317,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9741d1272c03c2cf7b925826113ebfdab81e05","tid":1271324,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到 其實勇武唔係唔得<br />\n但係要明白對抗一班齙牙癲犬 <br />\n係無可能咁易成功<br />\n唯一可行做法係圍完再退 再圍<br />\n挑釁癲犬情緒 令佢地使用不必要武力<br />\n係有鏡頭下 令佢地惡行無所遁形<br />\n先可以有效製造輿論壓力<br />\n而雞蛋就係最簡單而且最「暴力」挑撥毅進仔情緒<br />\n識衝識退 先係用腦嘅做法<br />\n我都好想令政府仆街<br />\n但問心 你勇武之餘 都要明白咁唔容易使港豬接受 <br />\n咁咪同目標背道而馳<br />\n各位勇者等你地平安光榮無憾回真正的家<br />\nBe water"},{"pid":"d84a51e77666fdbf83835427c5f8e74d6f09612f","tid":1271324,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb44bf45caa03329fb760235a071bdcb5540811","tid":1271324,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"bd3c8a60c92082013ba69aacb695d0c36bcf1d1e","tid":1271324,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"［向三毛五毛學習，分化藍絲第三集］每次活動後鼓吹失敗主義，用活動手法差異分化群眾，零晨留言引人互屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1271316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1271316</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0263fac3a153b8332bc533fdded58e730e6a7769","tid":1271324,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beb44bf45caa03329fb760235a071bdcb5540811","tid":1271324,"uid":73317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T06:30:29.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"bc001691d879fa9d5785112c1ed50da42dc12d53","tid":1271324,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7ae52d4a8d86f30849d113a5633f32650fbeeaf7","tid":1271324,"uid":174239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT